2	id: 004-breakdown-ux-to-screens
3	title: Breakdown UX to Screens
4	description: Extract screen definitions and sitemap from UX overview
5	skill: ux-breakdown
6	depends_on:
7	  - 003-generate-ux
8	tags:
9	  - screens
10	  - sitemap
